{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a8822d64-55a7-4236-99f5-31818186e774","content":"The `.testsettings` format is **legacy and ignored by modern MSTest**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how to migrate each part:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout=30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly load context | Default behavior now — no config needed |\n| Code Coverage collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01XkEZv2t4pugC5E9m2LVHET","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_019SDwjwA3MsmQk2Srvx5By8","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-05b603bfbe5e46d4824bb7d98f1faf87/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileTracingCollectorManager, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-05b603bfbe5e46d4824bb7d98f1faf87/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"44deeb13-2a55-4906-bf42-8aa06ca1a01e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file (legacy format) and has upgraded to MSTest 3.8.0. The `.testsettings` format is no longer supported by modern MSTest. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nLet me break do